c: 49
v: 13
t: "Adasamma, nokorﾎｵ sﾎｵ Yﾎｵ窶冀ﾍｻﾍｻ mo fri ﾍｻbarima (Adam) ne ﾍｻbaa (Hawa) mu, ﾎｵna Y窶兮yﾎｵ mo nntﾍｻn ne mmusua kuo sﾎｵdeﾎｵ mobehunu mo ho, (na mmom ﾎｵnnyﾎｵ sﾎｵ mobebu moho moho animtia). Nokorﾎｵ sﾎｵ mo mu onimuonyamfoﾍｻ wﾍｻ Nyankopﾍｻn hﾍｻ deﾎｵ ﾍｻne mo mu Nyamesuroni. Nokorﾎｵ sﾎｵ Nyankopﾍｻn ne Onimdefoﾍｻ, ﾆɚ́e Amanebﾍｻ Wura"